{"tid":171512,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得大家樂只有焗豬正嘅入嚟","createTime":"2017-03-25T11:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T14:20:23.000Z","uid":27083,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"940d66cb0a8d9aec264e40cb7d667a4fed00d9d1","tid":171512,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"冇左焗豬，我唔會再食大家樂<br />\n我自細去大家樂只會食焗豬<br />\n20年不變<br />\n有冇巴絲認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b191b6b57d4a2e9de6b57195b6b90c04e655882","tid":171512,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"有個排骨菜飯都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7b50471df92d2391a539f88001a0acc6f290f8","tid":171512,"uid":94935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"咖喱飯都正 其他狗食"},{"pid":"dd79fd093bfe878a9013c158a8a24ae3c1eec282","tid":171512,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"大家樂所有野都無大快活咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe98cfef7dcc83c2204c82be580558cb26a0a55","tid":171512,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人都追棒大家樂既焗豬，舊豬扒好難食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有塊蛋皮咁既野痴係個面。其他連鎖快餐店既焗豬好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f8c2a76ff9395fb3985a6dd610c24b05f935b8","tid":171512,"uid":48703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"咖哩牛腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6d7421fc3e1f866e857180810288ac0de74824","tid":171512,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re